snippet.title: Brayden Girard
snippet.description:
Husband and Father of two, CrossFit enthusiast, Web Design agency owner,  College professor and average gamer.... the Java keeps me going.

Here to create educational code and app tutorials, talk tech and hardware, play fun and live gaming content. 

Catch me live:  Mon - Thurs 10pm EST - https://caffeine.tv/JavaDad
